content:
Provide an intuitive, guided degree planning experience for your students. Learners can use the dynamic Intelligent Degree Planner to view their program requirements, search for eligible courses, and design their path to degree completion by session, term, and year.

They can add, remove, and rearrange their courses by dragging elements in an intuitive interface and create placeholders as needed. Students can submit the completed plans for approval and see status updates as their advisor reviews the plan.

This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Unlimited, and Developer editions where the Education Cloud license is enabled.

To offer Intelligent Degree Planning to your students, you need the Learner Success Experience Cloud license. Users with the Education Cloud Full Access permission set or the Education Cloud Limited Access permission set can set up the planner and create templates.
title: Intelligent Degree Planning in Education Cloud
